46:22.713 --> 46:24.815 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JEFFREY BROWN: Which is what?

46:24.849 --> 46:30.287 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
EDDIE HUANG: We just needed to
